### v134: Network-distance targeting (replacing hub-penalty)
- Hypothesis: hub_penalty too aggressive, prevents network expansion through chained junctions
- Change: replaced hub_penalty with network_penalty (min dist to any hub/friendly junction * 0.5)
- Also boosted expansion weight from 8.0/48 to 10.0/60
- First seed result: 4.67 (baseline avg 4.10)
- Running 5-seed comparison to validate
- v134 10-seed results: 6.70, 1.43, 0.00, 6.50, 9.95, 7.55, 3.33, 9.14, 5.43, 8.89
- v134 avg: 5.89 (up from 4.10 baseline, +44%)
- Seed 3 total wipeout (all agents died early, never recovered)
- Two seeds near/above 10: 9.95, 9.14

