### Key learnings
- Non-determinism is HUGE: same seed+code gives 0.00 to 6.70
- Need 20+ seeds for reliable comparisons
- Seed 3 is unwinnable (starter policy also scores 0.00)
- Heart batch increase can starve economy → wipeouts
- Budget changes are very sensitive — small tweaks cause big regressions
